{"tid":2037433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"攬炒嘅決心","createTime":"2020-05-27T03:37:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T05:17:16.000Z","uid":105167,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"9d23d9e88e537a3a25f572d9033bea72da7ff63a","tid":2037433,"uid":105167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:37:15.000Z","msg":"講一講背景先 <br />\n我老豆係一個和理非 但手足所有行為 佢都理解同支持 <br />\n但佢尋晚問左我一個問題 我完全唔識答<br />\n<br />\n老豆 ： 你聽日係咪出去？<br />\n我：你話呢<br />\n老豆：其實你係咪真心想攬炒？<br />\n我：寧為玉碎 不作瓦全！<br />\n老豆：咁如果張攬炒視為目標嘅話 惡歌法 國安法呢d 唔係應該由佢通過咩 等佢明目張膽咁摧毁一國兩制  <br />\n我：跟係啦 越早落實越好 一係就外國制裁一係就喳喳啉變新疆 大家攬炒<br />\n老豆：既然係咁 咁你聽日仲出去做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：............ <br />\n<br />\n此乃真實對話 個一刻我真係無言以對<br />\n利申 唔係分化/失敗撚/話人送頭 <br />\n只係覺得所有行為係咪都應該對應返本意同目的呢<br />\n不過 你問我有咩高見 我諗我同我老豆都唔識答<br />\n只係希望大家可以一齊討論下<br />\n而唔係一黎就話人送頭/當手足condom<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n民族自強 香港獨立"},{"pid":"64f1f86cb96048904c0ddf6d985c224b4091204b","tid":2037433,"uid":303422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:39:03.000Z","msg":"送頭與否佢都要夾硬過無計喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a927ff87cfbe87698bd69da1817b7c080bbb4dc8","tid":2037433,"uid":105167,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"64f1f86cb96048904c0ddf6d985c224b4091204b","tid":2037433,"uid":303422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:39:03.000Z","msg":"送頭與否佢都要夾硬過無計喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:47:56.000Z","msg":"咁我地應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9023588052cb818e63c6bba63329efc8a90a8ef","tid":2037433,"uid":262301,"